"" Author: Chris Meyers
"" ===========================================================================

" General ====================================================================
"" Disable beep and flash
set vb t_vb=

"" Default GUI size
set lines=35
set columns=140


" Key Mappings ===============================================================
"" <C-Tab> and <C-S-Tab> move between tabs
nnoremap <C-Tab> :tabnext<CR>
nnoremap <C-S-Tab> :tabNext<CR>

